Proprietors retain exclusive ownership of all intellectual property, tangible and intangible, including but not limited to: manuscripts, recordings, strategic documents, operational procedures, logos, trademarks, trade names, domain names, databases, software code, photography, video content, names, likenesses, financial information, and all derivative works.

### 1.2 Copyright Notice
All copyrightable works are protected under 17 U.S.C. § 102 et seq. Copyright © 2026 John Thompson and Lost Limb Riders, Inc. Registration numbers and statutory damages provisions apply.

### 1.3 No Waiver
No action, inaction, or course of dealing shall constitute a waiver of any rights under this Agreement or applicable law.

