Access is NON-TRANSFERABLE, NON-EXCLUSIVE, and REVOCABLE at any time without cause or notice.

### 3.2 Use Restrictions
Authorized users may access materials ONLY for:
- Internal organizational functions
- Board governance and decision-making
- Staff operational duties (within assigned scope)
- Volunteer training (limited to assigned program)
- Legal compliance and audit purposes

### 3.3 Prohibited Uses - Absolute Ban
Users are EXPRESSLY PROHIBITED from:
- Public disclosure, distribution, or sharing
- Commercial exploitation or monetization
- Posting to public repositories, websites, or platforms
- Sharing via email, cloud storage, or file-sharing services
- Copying for retention beyond employment/engagement
- Creating derivative works, adaptations, or modifications
- Extracting data, code, or content for external use
- Reverse engineering, decompiling, or disassembly
- Use in competing products, services, or organizations
- Use in educational materials without prior written consent
- Use in academic publications or research
- Use in podcast, video, or broadcast content
- Lending, sublicensing, or transferring to any third party
- Use after termination of employment or engagement

