### 4.1 Confidential Material
All materials in this repository are CONFIDENTIAL PROPRIETARY INFORMATION subject to strict confidentiality obligations.

### 4.2 Confidentiality Obligations
Users acknowledge and agree:
- Materials contain trade secrets under 18 U.S.C. § 1836
- Unauthorized disclosure constitutes trade secret misappropriation
- Disclosure triggers civil liability plus criminal penalties
- Obligation survives termination indefinitely

### 4.3 Requirement to Secure
Users must:
- Store materials only on secured, password-protected devices
- Use multi-factor authentication
