## 7. TERM & TERMINATION

### 7.1 Agreement Term
This Agreement is perpetual and binding.

### 7.2 Termination of Access
Proprietors may terminate access immediately:
- Upon notice of any breach
- Upon termination of employment or engagement
- For any reason or no reason
- Without liability or explanation

### 7.3 Obligations Upon Termination
Upon termination, user must:
- Immediately cease all use of materials
- Return or certify destruction of all copies within 5 business days
- Disable all access credentials immediately
- Cooperate with transition and audits
- Execute non-compete/non-solicitation agreements if required

Failure to comply constitutes material breach and triggers damages.

